Detailed Description

cvmx_eoi_endor_bistr_ctl_sta

EOI_ENDOR_BISTR_CTL_STA = EOI ENDOR BIST/BISR Control Status Register

Description: This register controls the BIST/BISR and reflects the final BISR/BIST status of ENDOR (BBP) memories.
